OL,3,CPolice make new arrest after alleged
OL,4,Carson attack on Jewish community
OL,5,Cambulances
OL,7,FPolice have made a new arrest in
OL,8,Fconnection with an alleged arson
OL,9,Fattack on four Jewish community
OL,10,Fambulances in London, the Crown
OL,11,FProsecution Service (CPS) said.
OL,13,FFour ambulances from Hatzola, a
OL,14,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,15,Foperating in the Golders Green area of
OL,16,Fnorth-west London, were set on fire in
OL,17,Fthe early hours of March 23, causing
OL,18,Fgas canisters stored in the vehicles
OL,19,Fto explode.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
