FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1775667952
OL,3,CPolice make new arrest after alleged
OL,4,Carson attack on Jewish community
OL,5,Cambulances
OL,7,FThe arrest was announced by prosecutor
OL,8,FEmma Harraway during a hearing at
OL,9,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FThe arrest was made at the court on
OL,13,FSaturday morning, Ms Harraway said.
OL,15,FIt comes as three males are due to
OL,16,Fappear at the court charged with arson
OL,17,Fbeing reckless as to whether life
OL,18,Fwould be endangered, in connection
OL,19,Fwith the alleged attack.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
