FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1775667952
OL,3,CPolice make new arrest after alleged
OL,4,Carson attack on Jewish community
OL,5,Cambulances
OL,7,FHamza Iqbal, 20, and Rehan Khan, 19,
OL,8,Fboth British nationals from Leyton,
OL,9,Fand a 17-year-old boy, a dual British
OL,10,Fand Pakistani national from
OL,11,FWalthamstow, were charged by the CPS
OL,12,Fon Friday following a Counter
OL,13,FTerrorism Policing investigation.
OL,15,FThe case is not being treated as
OL,16,Fterrorism but CTP said due to "the
OL,17,Fcircumstances of the incident" the
OL,18,Finvestigation is being led by its
OL,19,Fdetectives.
